Barcelona Tapas at their finest.  While on our honeymoon, we walked into Sensi around 2230 and it was completely full, but one of the servers asked us to wait and have a drink and she asked if were okay for us to sit at the bar which we were fine with!  The tuna tartare was probably one of the most amazing things I've ever eaten!  The seafood paella was perfect!  The ravioli was creamy and flavorful.  Dimly lit, romantic ambiance, delicious house wine, excellent service, would love to go back!  Reservations are highly recommended!!
